 S=\sin x + \sin(x+\alpha) +\sin(x+2\alpha) +\dots+\sin(x+n\alpha)
 S=\frac{\sin\frac{n+1}{2}\alpha\sin(x+\frac{n}{2}\alpha)}{\sin\frac{\alpha}{2}}
